Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯嘛 麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是襲名準備做得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一開始還納悶為什麼這孩子會是麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好開心 靈感不斷湧現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳得好 特別是小優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稱職的ACE 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}註：凪沙nagisa　智恵理chieri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,664)\fs30}nagi chie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究生也很有幹勁 特別是凪智恵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的進步顯著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova誕生之時 其他成員也閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果打算復活Center Nova制度 我會不擇手段地妨礙你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻平靜地說出這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 真見外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾是00的成員 不管何時 成員都團結一心 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心情 現在也和翼一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕不上電車了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 麻里子是襲名成員 有專車接送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也乘電車回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子 這樣可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,襲名成員對研究生異常地用心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和襲名成員還是研究生無關
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要按照我的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有女王氣質嘛 麻里子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我興奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好壞好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森麻里 也欺負欺負楚方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺負楚方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}好了 楚方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是優子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊 渦輪哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是有誰在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方的視力太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那種地方 做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲果然很美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麼大噪音的渦輪旁邊竟然也能聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但確實是優子的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子在傳達她的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使總選舉取得第一 她也沒有滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像要追求比現在更高的目標的呐喊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子的照片都收起來是不是太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是再貼出來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有優子的新生寫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有真琴的生寫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是可以便宜換給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴——子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu動作慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子要注意周圍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往Tomochin的位置過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛島老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我們自己稍微練習一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 我的練習強度不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 強度嚴重不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習中突然逃走的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知道什麼時候按快門才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我知道她確實是才華橫溢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的優子姐 雖然平時看似跟以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是偶爾會像剛才那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 總覺得有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像聖人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家一起歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大家所愛戴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻總覺得很難接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算處在大家之中也會覺得她高不可攀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是說啊醬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13代啊醬也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為Center Nova之後的一段時間裡 一直都是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪都不太接近他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發出讓人無法隨意搭話的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊醬你…好像漸漸地變得形單影隻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形單影隻? 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道 但是總有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家都是喜歡啊醬的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可以更依賴大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的啊醬 總感覺一直在一個人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜歡各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你為我擔心了 麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 我不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的孤獨到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊醬在那之後就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的Center Nova們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們到底消失到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果還能再見面的話 那到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火熱的太陽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕人的肌膚果然就是不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水嫩透白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪醬 好歹披個毛巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,663)}孤独はいつでも　自由のお代償に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論何時孤獨都是 獲取自由的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算付出巨大的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望前往那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會被任何人所妨礙之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖的Position 0
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Position 0…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該星球地表下蘊藏有豐富的雙晶素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 還有能激活雙晶素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使Kirara強烈閃耀的太陽之女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要感謝上蒼啊 甚至讓我想跳過即將要發生的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐好閃耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像真的習慣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐的話 一定可以成為Center Nova的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 成為Center Nova的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總選舉時 優子姐不是說過不會消失的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐的話 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova發生條件之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在秋葉星舉辦Live
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成為Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須能承受孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤獨?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 閃耀強大光芒的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要伴隨著更深的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被嫉妒 被敵視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Position 0就是背負這一切情感的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果能戰勝黑暗保持自我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能站上夢寐已久之處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候 眼前的位置一直屬於啊醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許正是她的身軀保護了我 讓我不被狂風捲走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後如今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼前空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請秋葉星居民儘快到掩體處避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避難?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES軍的大部隊越過了啟動中的防衛線 向這裡逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究生她們已經出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產生Center Nova的第二個條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣反常的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣象控制系統也許被黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方的秋葉星才不會是這樣電閃雷鳴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位上 為了守衛秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,織音 快脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 讓人著實捏了把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和承諾不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承諾?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼 這樣下去會危及到神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zodiac的目標是雙晶素和Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zodiac?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu Tomochin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著76期研究生保護神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神殿?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果先聖老師有什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00 不 整個秋葉星都會完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能讓你們得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 注意身後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨下得這麼大 淋得人好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家去劇場乘坐過的電車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起玩過的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家歌唱過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管遇到什麼恐慌 Center Nova都可以坦然應對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護成員們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 沒傷著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保護不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我閃耀不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Flying Get發射準備好沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概還需15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限你5分鐘之內準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:16:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪醬?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在演唱會上 AKB0048才能綻放最璀璨的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也是00最強的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這首曲子是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 繼續演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐 繼續演唱會?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是AKB0048
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是歌頌愛 舞動愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為愛而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了守護秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是咪醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都按計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產生Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一個條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴隨著戰鬥的生死攸關的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:18:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星 我們心靈的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡生活的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了自由而奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護秋葉星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著你多說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也趕到地下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃光導彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 大家趁現在快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的劇場在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三個發生條件已經全部具備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠缺的東風 正是那超越一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激烈的感情洪流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HIT! HIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中紅心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐 已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從秋葉星撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的目標是我們00
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再戰鬥下去只會徒增犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快坐上Flying Get暫時退避
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 秋葉星會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼會變成這樣
