Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人站在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裡能看見的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子 你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和啊醬約定好了
